lora推荐设置：

lora权重推荐：0.8-1都可以试试。

resolution：768*768;

items.name: SDXL FaeTastic Details
items.description:
This LoRA is used to enhance images, giving them more details, increasing saturation, and making things overall prettier and magical feeling. DO NOT USE IT WITH MY FAETASTIC SDXL MODEL, IT GETS FUNKY SINCE THAT MODEL HAS THIS BUILT IN, THIS LORA IS TO PUT THE 'FAETASTIC' EFFECT IN OTHER SDXL MODELS!!!!

I trained this LoRA on a bunch of my 1.5 generated images that I felt were high quality with resolution, color, and details... a lot of them involved my TIs which I think put a lot of 'magical' effect into it. This LoRA IS NOT realism focused.

I recommend a strength of .6-.8 for this model, otherwise, things can get a bit too strong....unless you want that effect. You can use Faetastic as a trigger word, but it doesn't really need it. :]

As always if anyone has any questions or needs troubleshooting with Civitai or my resources, you can always comment here or message me on Discord, I am in the Civitai discord.

Because I believe in the open-source spirit of SD, anyone is free to use this model or any of my LoRAs to merge or use as they see fit in an open-source sense, including selling any images or using them in personal projects. I would be extremely grateful to be credited for any merges or uses of my resources.

However, I am very opposed to having my model and resources I personally train and test and spend hundreds of hours on put up on third-party generation sites for their monetary gain where I receive nothing in return.

Megan Boone (born April 29, 1983) is an American actress. She is best known for her role as FBI agent and profiler Elizabeth Keen on the NBC drama series The Blacklist. She is a regular on Law & Order: LA and Blue Bloods and has appeared in films such as My Bloody Valentine 3D (2009) and Step Up Revolution (2012).

Boone was born in Petoskey, Michigan and raised in The Villages, Florida. Her parents relocated there when she was a child to be closer to her grandparents. Her grandfather, H. Gary Morse, was the developer of The Villages; and her mother, Jennifer Parr, is the Director of Sales. Boone says that she was "hooked" on acting at age seven when her grandparents took her to New York to see a Broadway play starring Nathan Lane.

Boone studied acting as a student at Belleview High School, where she graduated in 2001. In 2005, she graduated from Florida State University's School of Theatre with a Bachelor of Fine Arts (BFA) in Acting. Boone studied with Jane Alexander and Edwin Sherin at the Asolo Repertory Theatre and workshopped with playwright Mark Medoff. Boone credits Alexander with influencing her to continue acting though she considered quitting early in her career. In late 2017, Boone began studying for an MBA in Sustainability from Bard College.

items.name: CanKing's Artstyle LORA/LOCON
items.description:
PLEASE READ THIS BEFORE PUTTING THE LORA INTO YOUR FILE!!

在你用这个LORA之前请看这个

Due to I keep experimenting with this dataset, several model's architecture ( if that is the right way to call it ) are different, here is the following model with their own architecture :

由于我一直在试验这个数据集，几个模型的"架构"（如果这是正确的叫法的话）各不相同，以下是各自架构的模型：

26vp1 LOCON

26vp1-2 LOCON

26vp1-3 LOCON

26vp2 LORA

I recommend using 26vp2 or 26vp2-000016
我建议使用 26vp2或者26vp2-000016

Thought this LORA is pretty much a simpler one, with low amount of image dataset and cleaning, it still take ages for experimenting and stuffs. So if you wanted to support me, you can go through ko-fi and buying me a 2$ coffee ☕. I am planning to do models and other style or character LORA in the future.

Simple Description

This model will replicating CanKing, a Taiwanese artist and artist YouTuber's artstyle. It was trained with 26 image of recent CanKing's art.

It was trained with AnyLORA, so clearly it would work the best with AnyLORA. But it would be okay to use it for other anime model, at least I tried it on Counterfeit v3.
https://civitai.com/models/23900/anylora-checkpoint

When using, I suggested using DPM++ 2M Karras or DPM++ SDE Karras for sampling, and on the weightage between 0.6-1. Depends what you wanted. You can see and make up the most suitable weight for you with my plot XY.

And in bunches of generations, I realized 26vp1 family have higher chance of generating... weird stuff and text. All of my image generation do not getting the help of ControlNet, so in theory you could just, slap ControlNet OpenPose and negative prompt (text)

Also, use the CLIP skip 2 and I am not recommending anyone to run kl-f8-anime2 VAE onto 26vp1 family unless you really wanted to. Or else, see the XY plot that contain all of the 26vp1 family with blonde girl smoking cigarettes.

I originally thinking of releasing 16vp3 and 16vp4, but I realized, hell? it is so bad. So I decided to just release the 26 images dataset only.

Any problems with this LORA and stuffs? bang your comment in the comment below.


简单介绍

该模型将复制台湾画家和YouTuber 空罐王的风格。我使用了 26 张空罐王近期的作品图像进行训练。

它是用 AnyLORA 训练的，因此显然用 AnyLORA 效果最好。但我猜也可以用于其他动漫模型，至少我在 Counterfeit v3 上试过。

https://civitai.com/models/23900/anylora-checkpoint

使用的时后，我建议使用 DPM++ 2M Karras 或 DPM++ SDE Karras 进行采样，权重在 0.6-1 之间。您可以通过我的 XY 图查看并确定最适合您的权重。

在成批生成的过程中，我发现 26vp1 家族会出现一些奇怪的东西和文字。我要说我的所有图像生成都没有用到 ControlNet ，因此理论上你可以直接使用 ControlNet OpenPose 和负提示(text)。

此外，请使用 CLIP skip 2，我不建议你在 26vp1 系列上用 kl-f8-anime2 VAE来生成，除非你真的想这么做。否则，请参阅包含所有 26vp1 系列和金发女孩吸烟的 XY 图。

我原本想发布 16vp3 和 16vp4，但我用的过后觉得这。。。太烂的吧。所以我决定还是只发布 26 张图片版的LORA模型。

如果你对 这LORA或者其他的有任何问题或意见，请在下面的评论中发表您的伟大的想法或者问题。

items.name: Fairy Wings Lora #1
items.description:
This is the first Lora i ever trained. Its trained on Pixai.art where registered people can train Lora on their own without borrowing an high end PC from someone. Because i was not happy that the typical Model couldnt handle Fairy Wings well, i tried to train this lora to get constantly good Fairy Wings. I tested it on different weights but it seem 0.5 - 0.8 works the best without damaging your model type too much. As i mostly use Anime Models i only trained it for Anime Models, but you can try realistic, i wont make any promises for it.

Its trained on around 100 Images in different Styles and Ranges, from Landscape to Portrait, my tests seem to work okay but higher weights give the picture a bit of a very basic look, so as i said above, try to play around 0.5 - 0.8 weight. Please rate and comment how i can do better. Thats my first experience making a Lora.

(日本語説明は後半にあります)

Deformation expressions which are familiar in manga and anime-style can be reproduced.

Two variation types are available for "Comic 2" : (-_-) shaped.

  • Type 2-1

  • Type 2-2

  • To download both variations, switch version tabs ↑ above.

Helper prompt is recommended for Type 1 (Type 2 does not need such prompt).

  • Type 2-1 : Use with "closed eyes".

  • Type 2-2 : DO NOT use with "closed eyes".

Use with "IrisMix" checkpoint is recommended.

Other shaped eyes LoRA series will be available soon (already available on HuggingFace).

On my HuggingFace repo, you can download more various other LoRAs. please check it out.

https://huggingface.co/JujoHotaru/lora

漫画・アニメ的なデフォルメ表現の眼（デフォル眼）を各種再現できます。

「デフォル眼2」は (-_-) です。目の黒棒の端部形状の違いで2種類を用意しました。

  • Type 2-1

  • Type 2-2

すべての種類をダウンロードするには、ページ上部のバージョンタブを切り替えてください。

LoRAを適用するだけで使えますが、Type 1には補助プロンプトを追加することを推奨します。

  • Type 2-1 : "closed eyes" プロンプトを追加してください。

  • Type 2-2 : "closed eyes" プロンプトを追加しないでください。追加すると発動しにくくなります。

データモデルは"IrisMix"を推奨しています。

別形状の眼シリーズも順序公開予定です（HuggingFaceではすでに公開中です）。
